"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-sport-soccer-2024-0509-1448313-el-kaabi-strikes-twice-as-olympiacos-defeat-aston-villa\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  A composed Olympiacos outfit ended Aston Villa's European dreams in the semi-finals of the Europa Conference League.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13, \"end\": 23, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0141281847718645e-22, \"text\": \"Olympiacos\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 37, \"end\": 48, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.317533531665696e-23, \"text\": \"Aston Villa\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 100, \"end\": 117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.583704000422204e-32, \"text\": \"Conference League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Villa were eyeing a first European final since 1982 but, with the ancient Acropolis in the backdrop of the Stadio Georgios Karaiskakis, their hopes were in ruins after a 6-2 aggregate defeat.\", \"from\": 120, \"to\": 311, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 234, \"end\": 254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgios_Karaiskakis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4999954503241828e-29, \"text\": \"Georgios Karaiskakis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgios_Karaiskakis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgios_Karaiskakis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They travelled to Athens needing a Herculean effort to overturn a 4-2 deficit from the first leg, but limped to a 2-0 defeat on the night, with last week's hat-trick hero Ayoub El Kaabi scoring the goals which sent the Greek side through to their first European final.\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 581, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 331, \"end\": 337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"score\": 0.9999999984377155, \"rank\": 1.5620969564473533e-09, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\"}, {\"begin\": 484, \"end\": 498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ayoub El Kaabi\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\"}, {\"begin\": 532, \"end\": 537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9591299589162694, \"rank\": 0.04246754696908345, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympiacos owner Evangelos Marinakis, who also owns Nottingham Forest, was seen celebrating his club reaching the final across the city at the home of deadly rivals AEK Athens in three weeks.\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 583, \"end\": 593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0141281847718645e-22, \"text\": \"Olympiacos\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 600, \"end\": 619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evangelos_Marinakis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Evangelos Marinakis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evangelos_Marinakis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evangelos_Marinakis\"}, {\"begin\": 635, \"end\": 652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham_Forest_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1395811473368556e-34, \"text\": \"Nottingham Forest\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham_Forest_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham_Forest_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 748, \"end\": 751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AEK_Athens_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.966993123754208e-20, \"text\": \"AEK\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AEK_Athens_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AEK_Athens_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"score\": 0.9999999984377155, \"rank\": 1.5620969564473533e-09, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Villa's hopes of a comeback were effectively ended after just 10 minutes as El Kaabi extended Olympiacos' lead to the sound of a near-defeaning noise.\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 870, \"end\": 880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0141281847718645e-22, \"text\": \"Olympiacos\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Premier League side were sliced open by a long ball, former Wolves attacker Daniel Podence teed up Quini, whose cross was bundled home by El Kaabi.\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 932, \"end\": 946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.243989988546687e-26, \"text\": \"Premier League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\"}, {\"begin\": 1008, \"end\": 1022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Podence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daniel Podence\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Podence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Podence\"}, {\"begin\": 1031, \"end\": 1036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quini\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Quini\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Villa now had to find three goals just to send the tie to extra time and they had plenty of moments in the first half but were missing the quality when they needed it the most.\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1257, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Moussa Diaby broke through in the 30th minute after Leon Bailey had been fouled but home goalkeeper Kostas Tzolakis blocked his effort and then Douglas Luiz curled the free-kick over when play was brought back.\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1259, \"end\": 1271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moussa_Diaby\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Moussa Diaby\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moussa_Diaby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moussa_Diaby\"}, {\"begin\": 1311, \"end\": 1322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leon_Bailey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Leon Bailey\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leon_Bailey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leon_Bailey\"}, {\"begin\": 1403, \"end\": 1415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Luiz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Douglas Luiz\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Luiz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Luiz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tzolakis had to be at his best on the stroke of half-time to claw Bailey's deflected shot over as Villa pushed for one back before the break.\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1537, \"end\": 1543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\", \"score\": 0.9999999961924004, \"rank\": 2.957193690258985e-09, \"text\": \"Bailey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They went for it in the second with Jhon Duran tamely shooting at Tzolakis and Ezri Konsa heading over from a corner.\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1693, \"end\": 1703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezri_Konsa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ezri Konsa\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezri_Konsa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezri_Konsa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were becoming increasingly desperate, but still could not create any clear-cut chances and the hosts took advantage of big gaps at the back.\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1878, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And El Kaabi's fifth goal of the tie in the 81st minute killed it as he raced clear and drove the ball under Emiliano Martinez.\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 2007, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was initially ruled out for offside but VAR overturned the decision.\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2051, \"end\": 2054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.543408997293046e-40, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch Shamrock Rovers v St Patrick's Athletic in the League of Ireland on Friday from 7.35pm on RT\\u00c92 and RT\\u00c9 Player, follow a live blog on rte.ie/sport and the RT\\u00c9 News app      \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2087, \"end\": 2102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shamrock_Rovers_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.76513304872003e-23, \"text\": \"Shamrock Rovers\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shamrock_Rovers_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shamrock_Rovers_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 2108, \"end\": 2115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patrick_Star\", \"score\": 0.6884747633437989, \"rank\": 0.4426323731387446, \"text\": \"Patrick\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patrick_Star\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patrick_Star\"}, {\"begin\": 2177, \"end\": 2181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c92\", \"score\": 0.9994238889060038, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c92\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c92\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c92\"}, {\"begin\": 2186, \"end\": 2189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9835396432123026, \"rank\": 0.013767790549921992, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"